    "description": "<p>Mectec Engineering Pte Ltd was incorporated in year 2006 as a multi-disciple engineering company for construction industries. Our company major fabrication and installation of Piping systems (carbon steel, stainless steel and duplex) and machine components.</p>\n<p>Mectec has 15 years of experience with good track record on piping installation for various system at major industrial projects. Mectec has successfully completed major fast track project in Data Center and Semiconductor Industry.</p>\n<p>We have a team of well trained and experience direct workforce.</p>\n<p>Mectec has been certificate Biz Safe Star, ISO 45001:2018 and ISO 9001:2015.</p>\n<p><u><strong>Company's Capabilities</strong></u></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Piping system Fabrication and Installation</li>\n  <li>Plant and Machinery Installation</li>\n  <li>Steel Structural Fabrication and Installation</li>\n  <li>Precision Machining</li>\n</ul>",
